PMjNmRM%3D&h=3098c7d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.microsoft.com/2016/05/18/microsoft-selling-feature-phone-business-to-fih-mobile-ltd-and-hmd-global-oy/</a><br />\n<br />\nM$係將前功能手機部賣咗俾FIH﹐當中包括生產線、工廠、工人、生產技術等轉哂俾FIH﹐而原有M$ mobile嘅員工就過哂去HMD﹐所以HMD而家班高層主管基本上就係Nokia mobile/ M$ mobile嘅人。而nokia 品牌使用權即時退返俾nokia<br />\n<br />\nNokia confirms that the strategic agreement covering branding rights and intellectual property licensing with HMD Global Oy (HMD), originally announced on May 18, 2016 has come into force.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nokia.com/en_int/news/releases/2016/12/01/nokia-brand-licensee-hmd-global-is-now-the-new-home-of-nokia-phones\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nokia.com%2Fen_int%2Fnews%2Freleases%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2Fnokia-brand-licensee-hmd-global-is-now-the-new-home-of-nokia-phones&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCxwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=732a23c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nokia.com/en_int/news/releases/2016/12/01/nokia-brand-licensee-hmd-global-is-now-the-new-home-of-nokia-phones</a><br />\n<br />\nnokia收返品牌使用權之後就將使用權交俾HMD﹐HMD可以使用十年用於生產電話/平板﹐品牌授權係唔關鴻海/FIH事。"},{"pid":"90573985312928fba043d5d1bb82d9ebe4623dc9","tid":544033,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"12c473806133379bc0023f5af71ec49feed57a05","tid":544033,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9650021cf56e44116811b8ca0bee773de95a898","tid":544033,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b3c4bee5f90d8b3974b0837849418de179bd3a9","tid":544033,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:35:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20160519000929-260303\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fnewspapers%2F20160519000929-260303&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCxwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d9e16dcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20160519000929-260303</a><br />\n我GOOGLE下就搵到依個 有冇再新D既消息?"}