%2Fen_int%2Fnews%2Freleases%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2Fnokia-brand-licensee-hmd-global-is-now-the-new-home-of-nokia-phones&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCxwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=732a23c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nokia.com/en_int/news/releases/2016/12/01/nokia-brand-licensee-hmd-global-is-now-the-new-home-of-nokia-phones</a><br />\n<br />\nnokia收返品牌使用權之後就將使用權交俾HMD﹐HMD可以使用十年用於生產電話/平板﹐品牌授權係唔關鴻海/FIH事。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T17:05:10.000Z","msg":"你有料過果個 我信住你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7f04f2b92c069caab487cf8a8b8b125aa99740","tid":544033,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d39eca5ac4a7e0e596e590bcd9fe9e0b7e10ea5","tid":544033,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d00b11dc59580c3dff9393eb21b637f0016f8ac0","tid":544033,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9650021cf56e44116811b8ca0bee773de95a898","tid":544033,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:42:48.000Z","msg":"睇少喲台灣喲吹水新聞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nM$邊有權轉賣nokia 個brand啊大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢一樣嘢真係錯到離哂譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"又叫我GOOGLE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  跟住又唔講D得你知既野比我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:51:02.000Z","msg":"原來你連google都唔識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁維基你識用啦啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T17:05:46.000Z","msg":"就算WIKI都唔好睇中文版﹐班台仔以為nokia收緊皮﹐以為要不是郭台銘救nokia﹐nokia一早就完蛋了而打哂飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHMD Global Oy, branded as HMD, is a Finnish company affiliated with Nokia. Operating since December 2016, the firm develops and markets smartphones and feature phones under the &quot;Nokia&quot; brand name. The company has exclusive rights to the brand for mobile phones through a licensing agreement.[5] It was created by inheriting Microsoft Mobile's feature phone business, which was sold by Nokia in 2014. They are in a &quot;close partnership&quot; with Google and use the Android software on their smartphones,[6] whereas on their feature phones the Series 30+ platform is mainly used.[7] The HMD brand is only used for corporate purposes and does not appear in advertising, whereas the name Nokia Mobile is used on social media.[8][9]<br />\n<br />\nHMD is headquartered in Espoo, opposite Nokia's head office, and the company is largely staffed by former Nokia executives.[10] The CEO was Arto Nummela, a Nokia veteran for 17 years, until July 2017 when President Florian Seiche took over as CEO.[11] Manufacturing is outsourced to Foxconn.[12][13][14] Nokia has no investment in HMD but remains a partner, setting mandatory requirements and providing patents and technologies, in return for royalty payments.[15][16] HMD use a marketing strategy advertising the Nokia phones as &quot;pure, secure and up to date&quot; (referring to a stock Android interface and its commitment to fast updates) as well as brand trust and nostalgia.[17][18][19][20]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HMD_Global\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FHMD_Global&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCxwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=cfa79b34\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HMD_Global</a>"},{"pid":"671c57c1d1976f55716869c6afa547bc2d98f295","tid":544033,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa7f04f2b92c069caab487cf8a8b8b125aa99740","tid":544033,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d39eca5ac4a7e0e596e590bcd9fe9e0b7e10ea5","tid":544033,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,