 advertising the Nokia phones as &quot;pure, secure and up to date&quot; (referring to a stock Android interface and its commitment to fast updates) as well as brand trust and nostalgia.[17][18][19][20]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HMD_Global\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FHMD_Global&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCxwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=cfa79b34\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HMD_Global</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T17:12:49.000Z","msg":"我正想講睇埋WIKI都睇唔到D咩 得2016 5月18日前既野"},{"pid":"8af03f189f620240a3b12e4b3e8f4b06bae62556","tid":544033,"uid":61954,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7fdffcea25b30971fe5102576b40d9c608439bc","tid":544033,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d39eca5ac4a7e0e596e590bcd9fe9e0b7e10ea5","tid":544033,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d00b11dc59580c3dff9393eb21b637f0016f8ac0","tid":544033,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"又叫我GOOGLE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  跟住又唔講D得你知既野比我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:51:02.000Z","msg":"原來你連google都唔識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁維基你識用啦啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:57:26.000Z","msg":"係咁話唔係 又比唔到野我睇 跟住又叫我搵過 <br />\n我搵比你又話係假野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T17:16:53.000Z","msg":"我幾時話係假嘢<br />\n你唔好老屈呀"},{"pid":"58db0072336ff92349da4a8bd5ac2ae075a06166","tid":544033,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b3c4bee5f90d8b3974b0837849418de179bd3a9","tid":544033,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a53d97eb2805452400f18eed9bc5d2d7e448e052","tid":54403